{"tid":251132,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"(貓)發動技能討論post","createTime":"2017-05-20T15:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T14:33:21.000Z","uid":7049,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3642068806ba13b42f629adf9bb0118cc6309523","tid":251132,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"有領養攻略 又有人會問邊度買貓好<br />\n而家又係貓既出生高峰潮 不如我地討論下點發動技能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先注意：冇經驗同冇時間 千祺唔好執奶貓B</span></span><br />\n要2-4hrs 餵一次奶 喂到戎奶都成兩個月<br />\n絕對唔岩上班一族同冇湊貓B經驗既人（好易死千祺唔好唔好搏）<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n常備少量貓糧放係袋，罐會吸引力大d特別係魚味<br />\nsupermarket有得賣 <br />\n(唔建議收服左長期再餵，味精重又咸同唔健康）<br />\n夜晚多數機會較大<br />\n留意草叢邊果d暗位 唔好掛住玩電話<br />\n可以試下上youtube播貓叫聲<br />\n<br />\n當搵到有目標既地方就可以餵一段時間<br />\n觀察下佢怕唔怕人<br />\n由體型會唔會太大（成貓好多時入左屋都好難習慣，由佢係返戶外啦）<br />\n<br />\n如果一段時間都friend到 就可以準備野去發動技能<br />\n但因為我只係餵過浪貓 依一part有錯請指點<br />\n<br />\n準備籠（執笠倉都有得買 80蚊度）<br />\n食物要香既重味 引佢入籠<br />\n用火燒魷魚絲係d貓義工講既方法 話好多時都引到貓<br />\n手套厚個d 怕整親手 最好包到手前臂<br />\n<br />\n咁一但引到佢地入去就可以開心做貓奴<br />\n記得要帶佢地去睇醫生做個body check <br />\n冇問題就可以正式做奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好再受異工氣<br />\n發動唔到就去spca啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有錯請指點呀！！"},{"pid":"6ddc05dd892a92bae35f87ce92b11a5247f2f914","tid":251132,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T15:54:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a672847226a69e34cecb9b1075a70a57bba0385","tid":251132,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/235419_e3bf6825f5cabfecc9c3ba57cb963b8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F235419_e3bf6825f5cabfecc9c3ba57cb963b8f.jpg&h=e1a47edd&s={SIZE}\" />點解成日有貓跟住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你生得似佢地老母"},{"pid":"df58ba665dd601f7941789c87d9e0d98f1963ea7","tid":251132,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c839e3497d7aaae5581673d90704361d9e469333","tid":251132,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:06:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/235419_e3bf6825f5cabfecc9c3ba57cb963b8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F235419_e3bf6825f5cabfecc9c3ba57cb963b8f.jpg&h=e1a47edd&s={SIZE}\" />點解成日有貓跟住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你生得似佢地老母</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你生得似小二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58aa83c9a04a3e06ece401ad728611689502ea76","tid":251132,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/235419_e3bf6825f5cabfecc9c3ba57cb963b8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F235419_e3bf6825f5cabfecc9c3ba57cb963b8f.jpg&h=e1a47edd&s={SIZE}\" />點解成日有貓跟住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬鞍山有隻同相中類似野貓唔見左兩星期<br />\n我同佢成日玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時餵開個嬸又搵唔到佢<br />\n佢又好驚人應該唔係俾人收養左"},{"pid":"bef8819ce1325e4edbe1a6858a368f25016ec914","tid":251132,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T06:58:18.000Z","msg":"又係剪左左耳<br />\n係唔係馬鞍山影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eee139f0d0da8bfdeb29f3d1436da5522366039","tid":251132,"uid":7954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28aa17737b8f27b174fa77c9fee66e31c4f5e1d7","tid":251132,"uid":52227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"之前見個義工用脆香雞翼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香到我都想食"}]}